,"link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":6719,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/20\/abu-bakr-khalifah-imam-salat\/","url_meta":{"origin":8243,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Khilafah: The Prophet orders Abu Bakr to lead prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 20, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Musa reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, became ill, and when his condition was critical, he said, \u201cTell Abu Bakr to lead the people in prayer.\u201d Aisha said, \u201cHe is a soft-hearted man. He will not be able to lead in your place.\u201d The Prophet said\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":6104,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/09\/sahabah-first-abu-bakr\/","url_meta":{"origin":8243,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Companions: First Muslims were slaves, women, Abu Bakr","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 9, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"'Ammar reported: I saw the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, while there was no one with him but fives slaves, two women, and Abu Bakr. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 3460 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Bukhari \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0645\u064e\u0651\u0627\u0631 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0623\u064e\u064a\u0652\u062a\u064f \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u065